    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="uv-vis-diffuse-reflectance-spectroscopy-紫外可见光漫反射光谱"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#uv-vis-diffuse-reflectance-spectroscopy-紫外可见光漫反射光谱"></a> Uv-Vis Diffuse Reflectance Spectroscopy （紫外可见光漫反射光谱）</h1><h2 id="1-简介"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1-简介"></a> 1. 简介</h2><p>物质对光线的响应可分为两类：反射（Remission)和透射(Transmission)。Remission是物质对光产生的反射或背散射作用，transmission是则是光线穿过物质的过程。</p><p>物质在受到的光线照射后，其表面发生镜面散射或漫反射。漫反射过程中，物质对特定<br />波长的光线产生吸收特征。这种吸收特征关于波长连续化，得到漫反射光谱。在不同光谱区间，漫反射光谱能得到固体表面的不同特征。</p><h2 id="光谱的数学处理"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#光谱的数学处理"></a> 光谱的数学处理</h2><p>1862年，George Gabriel Stokes发表了基于层叠结构对反射和透射定量的公式。该公式将物质分为 n 层，每层对光线有特定的吸收 (a)，反射®和透射(t)分数，且三数和 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a+r+t=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.61508em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">t</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span> ，对于每一层，可表示为：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>A</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>T</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{ A_n,R_n, T_n}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8777699999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.151392em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">n</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.151392em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.00773em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">n</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><spa